data.description: Large home with plenty of bedrooms located just outside of Mentone. The property features almost 4000 sq. ft. of finished area, 5 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, first floor master bedroom, a large living room and family room with fireplaces, inground pool, and more. Master bedroom has master bath with large walk-in shower, walk in closet, jet tub, and French doors to a deck. The pool area has a master grill covered with gazebo and a pool house with bathroom. This is a custom-built solar home with 10-inch staggered walls designed for no loss of heat or cooling, very efficient.
